Package: FireBehaviourCalcsR
Title: Australian Fire Behaviour Prediction Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kevin", "Tolhurst", role = "aut",
           comment = "Original spreadsheet author, University of Melbourne"),
    person("Liu", "Zhao", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "liu.zhao@utas.edu.au"),
    person("Grant J", "Williamson", role = c("aut", "cre", "ths"),
           email = "grant.williamson@utas.edu.au"))
Author: Kevin Tolhurst [aut], Liu Zhao [aut, cre],
    Grant J Williamson [aut, cre,ths]
Maintainer: Liu Zhao <liu.zhao@utas.edu.au>
Description: A collection of Australian fire behaviour prediction models
    translated from the Advanced Fire Behaviour Prediction Standard Workbook
    (Tolhurst, 2007-2016). Includes McArthur Mk5 Forest, VESTA, CSIRO
    Grassland, Heathland (Anderson et al. 2015), Buttongrass
    (Marsden-Smedley 2003), WA Red Book (Beck 1995), WA Mallee (McCaw 1998),
    Mallee-Heath (Cruz et al. 2013), suppression resource calculators, and
    supporting meteorological utilities.
